+# Dynamic Model Router
+
+Chooses *k* providers per policy, enforces **budget** and **latency** caps, gathers generations and emits rich **metadata** used by consensus & provenance.
+
+- Config: `policies/providers.yml`
+- Module: `src/ecl/router.py`
+- Adds `diversity_score`, `budget_spent_usd`, `route_id` to API response.
+
+## Guardrails
+- **PII**: per-provider `allow_pii` + pre-send redaction opportunity.
+- **Budget/latency**: `budget_usd`, `max_latency_ms` constraints.
+- **Health & failover**: adapters raise `ProviderError`; router proceeds.
+- **Schema & calibration**: response includes `x-schema-version`; keep ECE/Brier tracking per-provider downstream.
+
+## Try it
+```bash
+export OPENROUTER_API_KEY=...
+uvicorn src.ecl.server.app:app --reload
+curl -s localhost:8000/verify | jq .
+```
+
